description.en: The Money Market Index (MMI) is an index token of the top stablecoins distributed across variable-rate, peer-to-peer, and fixed-rate lending protocols on Ethereum. Within the index, USDC, DAI, and USDT are deposited into the most battle-tested money market protocols.
